            <div id="message">
                <h3>Our Message</h3>
                <p>Our team set out to create an adorable cat themed game in the popular match-3 made famous by games such as Candy Crush and Bejeweled. Similarly to these famous games, our game rewards players with a rush of dopamine for each match of 3, 4, and 5 cat tiles.</p>
            </div>
